Description:
Under Offer
Enviably positioned in one of Keilor East's premier pockets, this stunning new 4BR residence provides the ultimate modern family lifestyle with its architectural excellence, floorplan versatility and premium inclusions throughout. Quality at every turn, the home's beautifully appointed interior showcases alternate master bedrooms on each level (both with fitted WIRs and deluxe ensuites), two additional bedrooms (also with fitted robes), equally-impressive main bathroom and guest powder room (fourth WC). Add to this a dedicated study area, central lounge (upstairs) and light-filled open-plan living/dining area accompanied by a gourmet kitchen with Bosch appliances, ample cupboard space and walk-in pantry. Along with soft-close cabinetry and stone benchtops throughout (including the laundry), the home also includes zoned ducted heating and refrigerated cooling for year-round comfort, alarm and video intercom, along with excellent storage options, on-trend black fittings, premium carpets and European oak timber floors, floor-to-ceiling tiles (all bathrooms) and recessed cisterns (all WCs). Stacker doors reveal a substantial entertaining deck and north-facing back garden, plus the added appeal of an internally-accessed garage (r/c) and additional driveway parking. Walking distance to Centreway shops and cafes, local buses and a range of primary and secondary schools (including PEGS), it's also close to Steele Creek trails and acres of parkland as well as immediate access to the Calder Freeway.

Spacious Living With Investment Appeal

Stroll to Milleara Shopping Centre, buses, schools and parklands, while airports and freeways are easily accessible.

Description:
A beautiful family environment
With modern day comforts, size and old world charm all in perfect harmony this amazing home would prove ideal for a growing family. The home features a massive master bedroom with ensuite and a further three bedrooms, lounge and dining room, a large well equipped kitchen, with a solid "Falcon Cooker" as a central focal point, and meals area that extends to a delightful rumpus room. Set on a big, leafy block, the home includes ducted heating, air conditioner, alarm, three water tanks and a serene big undercover entertaining area. A 616sq. metre parcel of land, established gardens, brick pavements and a sprinkle of old world fittings and fixtures further enhance the allure of this outstanding property; conveniently located near Schools, Keilor Shopping centre, public transport, Ring Road and Calder Freeway.

Description:
Auction this Saturday at 1pm
Scenic Views!
Elegantly perched in a private residential court within a stones throw away from parklands is this 5 bedroom home. Ground floor offers formal lounge and dining room off the wide entry hall flowing onto the open plan kitchen (with 900mm gas cooktop and dishwasher), meals and living. Ascend the timber staircase to reveal a retreat, balcony and 4 further bedrooms, master with WIR & ensuite, others with built in robes and serviced by the family bathroom and separate W.C. Flowing outdoors youll see a generous pergola expanding from the remote controlled drive through double garage connecting the additional garage/workshop yet leaving plenty of yard space for the kids and pets to mingle. Features: 2.7m ceilings, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, 3 x air-conditioners, powder room, ample storage, laundry, garden shed, gazebo and more. You will certainly be impressed with the flowing floor plan synced with current day fittings throughout. Dont miss this opportunity, be sure to view it.
